import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { ChildrenOutletContexts } from '@angular/router'; import { slideInAnimation } from '../../route-animations'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.scss'] }) export class AppComponent { constructor(private contexts: ChildrenOutletContexts) {} getRouteAnimationData() { return this.contexts.getContext('primary')?.route?.snapshot?.data?.['animation']; } }
